  - m_Id: 7300000000001
    m_Localized: Labor Union Drive
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7300000001001
    m_Localized: Worker representatives are organizing across shifts. Daily credit
      deductions may apply until the dispute is settled.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7300000000002
    m_Localized: Wartime Mobilization
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7300000001002
    m_Localized: Supply shocks and priority requisitions are squeezing procurement
      and delivery windows. Expect volatile costs and tighter lead times.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7300000000003
    m_Localized: Automation Program
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7300000001003
    m_Localized: The board has approved a major automation push. Retooling will reshape
      throughput, maintenance load, and staffing plans over the coming quarters.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7300000000004
    m_Localized: Collective Bonus Demand
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7300000001004
    m_Localized: Workers demand a one-time collective bonus payment.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7300000000005
    m_Localized: Overtime Pilot Program
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7300000001005
    m_Localized: Union negotiators insist on adopting the overtime pilot program.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7300000000006
    m_Localized: Wood Supply Request
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7300000001006
    m_Localized: Union requests wood supplies for break-room renovations.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7300000000007
    m_Localized: Safety Equipment Supplies
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7300000001007
    m_Localized: Workers demand safety equipment shipments to prevent workplace accidents.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7300000000008
    m_Localized: Break Room Furniture
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7300000001008
    m_Localized: Union requests basic furniture to furnish worker relaxation areas.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7300000000009
    m_Localized: Winter Warm Clothing
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7300000001009
    m_Localized: Workers request basic warm clothing to survive the cold season.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7300000000010
    m_Localized: Welfare Fund Contribution
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7300000001010
